('Dark Souls III', 'As fires fade and the world falls into ruin, journey into a universe filled with more colossal enemies and environments. Players will be immersed into a world of epic atmosphere and darkness.', 'https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/374320/header.jpg', 59.99, 0, 70000, 88, 600000, 89, 43, '2016-04-12'),
